{"bangumi":{"date":"1989-08-27","platform":"TV","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/57/7c/100651_V6V9c.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/57/7c/100651_V6V9c.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/57/7c/100651_V6V9c.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/57/7c/100651_V6V9c.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/57/7c/100651_V6V9c.jpg"},"summary":"　　这部作品是《24小时电视节目 用爱拯救地球》系列特别动画中的第12部作品。内容分为两个部分：前半部分是手塚治虫的回忆录，讲述了他在少年时观看中国动画电影《铁扇公主》后深受启发，与孙悟空相遇并开始走上为动漫事业奋斗一生的道路的故事；后半部分则以公元3010年的银河系蓝宝石星为背景，呈现出一部全新的科幻版《西游记》。然而该作品的构思尚未完成，手塚治虫就突然离世，这部作品也成为了他的遗作之一。","name":"手塚治虫物語 ぼくは孫悟空","name_cn":"手塚治虫物语 我是孙悟空","tags":[{"name":"1989","count":12,"total_cont":0},{"name":"手冢治虫","count":12,"total_cont":0},{"name":"TV","count":12,"total_cont":0},{"name":"漫画改","count":10,"total_cont":0},{"name":"剧场版","count":8,"total_cont":0},{"name":"手塚治虫","count":7,"total_cont":0},{"name":"波多正美","count":6,"total_cont":0},{"name":"TVspecial","count":6,"total_cont":0},{"name":"りんたろう","count":5,"total_cont":0},{"name":"西游记","count":5,"total_cont":0},{"name":"草尾毅","count":5,"total_cont":0},{"name":"竟然有动画","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"童年","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"奇幻","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"日本动画","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"TVSP","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"田中真弓","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"四分","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"百濑义行","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"林重行","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"清水マリ","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"松原德弘","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"山下久仁明","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"旧物","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"1989年","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"漫改","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"日本","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"1980s","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"手塚プロダクション","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"OVA","count":1,"total_cont":0}],"infobox":[{"key":"中文名","value":"手塚治虫物语 我是孙悟空"},{"key":"别名","value":[{"v":"手冢治虫物语 我的孙悟空"},{"v":